## 3. Frontend Pages Integration
- [x] **Onboard Page (`/onboard`)**: Store the form locally. When user "Signs up", execute `organizationService.save()`, fetch the returned `org_id` (UUID), and store it in `localStorage`.
- [x] **Discover Page (`/discover`)**: Fetch `org_id` from local storage. Pass it to the discovery endpoint. Map the returned list of grants from `backend-2` dictionary format into the UI state.
- [x] **Grant Details (`/grant/[id]`)**: Refactor so the "Apply with AI" button calls `POST /applications/create` first to initialize an application dynamically in the database.
- [x] **Proposal Studio (`/apply/[id]`)**: Since the route parameter is now an `app_id` (not just evaluating generic grants), update the interface to fetch the specific DRAFT application context from the database and populate the studio answers.
- [x] **Overview / Applications (`/applications`)**: Refactor to dynamically list applications from the Supabase DB matching the active `org_id`.
- [x] **Dashboard (`/dashboard`)**: Map database pipeline logic into dashboard visual charts.

